  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lufiilya Cooperative Development</narrative>
  </title>
  <description akvo:type="5" type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lufiilya irrigation scheme is one of the biggest schemes in Karonga. The farmers in this irrigation scheme have been supported for increased rice production and rice marketing through cooperative development. The project aims at scaling up the extent of the activities. The overall objective of the project is to increase farmer&apos;s income through the rice value chain development. The project will further support the Cooperative to join the Rice Union for collective rice marketing.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description akvo:type="4" type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ngerenge Rice Cooperative  in Malawi</narrative>
  </description>
  <description akvo:type="6" type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The lead organization /partner  in this intervention of Ngerenge rice cooperative  development project of Luffilya scheme is CISP. For sustainability of project activities, CISP is working with Karonga District Agriculture Development Office (DADO),National Rice Platform and Irrigation Department.
The overall objective of the intervention is enabling smallholder rice farmers to generate greater income within the rice value chain through participation in Ngerenge Cooperative .</narrative>
  </description>
